instructions: Put the dinner plate on the table cloth
Put the salad plate on the dinner plate<br>
Place the napkin on top of the salad plate.
Place the wine glass on the top right corner of the table cloth.
Place the water glass to the right of and slightly below the wine glass.
Place the salad fork to the left of the dinner plate.
Place the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork.
Place the dinner knife to the right of the dinner plate.
Place the soup spoon to the right of the dinner knife.
